# Development Workflow & Standards

## Tech Stack

- **Vue 3** + Composition API + TypeScript
- **Nuxt 3** (SSR, auto-imports)
- **CSS Variables** — No Tailwind, BEM naming

## 📁 CSS Structure

```
/assets/styles/
├── variables.css    # USER ONLY (colors, fonts, spacing, accents) *(this file can use px)*
├── reset.css        # HTML element resets
├── utilities.css    # Reusable classes (.card, .container, etc.)
├── button.css       # Base button styles
├── form.css         # Base form styles
├── animations.css   # Animations
└── main.css         # Import order
```

## 🎨 CSS Variables Usage

### **variables.css** (USER ONLY - Can't Modify in any case)

**Background Colors**: Use `--main-color-*`, `--accent-*`
**Font Colors**: Use `--color-white`, `--main-color-*`
**Font Size**: Use `--font-[xs/s/m/lg/xl]` only
**Spacing Margin/Padding/Gap**: Use `--gap-[xs/sm/md/lg/xl]` only

