## 🏗️ Clean Code Principles

### **Zero waste class attributes and property**

- All .css files must correspond to variables.css
- All html elements and css classes must have corresponding css classes to .css files
- Use BEM naming convention for all CSS classes
- Follow the pattern: `.block` `.block-element` `.block-modifier`

### **HTML Example**

```html
<div class="[example-name]">
  <div class="[example-card] card hover-lift"></div>
</div>
```

### **CSS Example**

```css
.[example-card] {
  background-color: var(--main-color-1);
  color: var(--color-white);
}
```

### **Utilities Example**

```css
.card {
  border: 1px solid var(--main-color-8);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--gap-lg);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}
```

